title: Game Theory and Money Week 3
itunes:title: Game Theory and Money Week 3
description:
In the Week 3 edition of Game Theory and Money, Cynthia Frelund and Matt "Money" Smith break down a week of home underdogs around the NFL, project whether or not the Dallas Cowboys and Denver Broncos are "pretenders" or "contenders", and give you picks for who will win each of the 15 games played this weekend and on Monday night in Week 3.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
